text.div:
This code system http://ibm.com/fhir/cdm/CodeSystem/match-confidence-level defines the following codes:

CodeDisplay
no-match This record is not likely to be a match. This record should ONLY be matched when another match is used to identify the match or if a human has intervened to specify a match.

name: MatchConfidenceLevelCodeSystem
title: Match Confidence Level Codes
description: Codes indicating confidence level of matched entities

concept.display: This record is not likely to be a match.  This record should ONLY be matched when another match is used to identify the match or if a human has intervened to specify a match.
